"grunt" - http://gruntjs.com/ (The JavaScript Task Runner)

# Linux (Debian / Ubuntu)
sudo aptitude install ruby-full build-essential nodejs

# Windows
http://rubyinstaller.org/
http://nodejs.org/download/

gem update --system
npm install -g grunt-cli
npm install -g grunt-init

-----------------------------

1) HowTo -> run a job

1.1) install packages from "package.json"

  npm install

1.2.1)  ... and run "grunt" for all jobs ...

  grunt build

1.2.2) ... or "grunt watch" for watching file-changes ...

  grunt watch
